                <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: 07/14/2025</p>

                <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
                <p>RebateAZ ("we," "us," or "our") is a rebate program operated under Home Smart, a licensed real estate brokerage. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your personal information when you interact with our services, including SMS/text messaging (A2P 10DLC), website, and rebate program.</p>
                <p>By participating in our rebate program or opting into our communications, you consent to the practices described in this policy.</p>

                <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
                <p>We may collect the following information:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Name, phone number, email, and property address.</li>
                    <li><strong>Transaction Details:</strong> Rebate requests, purchase agreements, and eligibility verification.</li>
                    <li><strong>Communication Data:</strong> SMS/text interactions, customer service inquiries, and opt-in records.</li>
                    <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address, device information, and website usage (via cookies).</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p>We use your information to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Process rebate requests and verify eligibility.</li>
                    <li>Communicate via SMS/text (A2P 10DLC), email, or phone regarding your rebate status.</li>
                    <li>Improve our services and customer experience.</li>
                    <li>Comply with legal and regulatory requirements.</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>4. SMS/Text Messaging (A2P 10DLC Compliance)</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Consent:</strong> By opting in, you agree to receive transactional and promotional SMS messages from RebateAZ.</li>
                    <li><strong>Frequency:</strong> Message frequency varies based on rebate status and requests.</li>
                    <li><strong>Opt-Out:</strong> Reply STOP to unsubscribe at any time. For help, reply HELP.</li>
                    <li><strong>Carrier Fees:</strong> Standard message and data rates may apply.</li>
                    <li><strong>Data Protection:</strong> We use secure platforms compliant with TCPA and CTIA guidelines.</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>5. Sharing Your Information</h2>
                <p>We may share data with:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Home Smart agents & affiliates (for rebate processing).</li>
                    <li>Service providers (SMS platforms, CRM tools).</li>
                    <li>Legal authorities (if required by law).</li>
                </ul>
                <p>We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>

                <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
                <p>We implement industry-standard measures (encryption, access controls) to protect your data. However, no method is 100% secure.</p>

                <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Access/Update:</strong> Request your data by contacting us.</li>
                    <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion, subject to legal obligations.</li>
                    <li><strong>Opt-Out:</strong> Unsubscribe from SMS/texts anytime (reply STOP).</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p>We may update this policy periodically. The latest version will be posted on our website.</p>

